# Force LF line endings on checkout for all text files, on every OS.
# Without this, Windows checks files out with CRLF, which breaks LF-sensitive
# parsing (e.g. the SKILL.md frontmatter regex) and makes goldens/byte-compares
# differ between platforms. text=auto lets git auto-detect binary files and
# leave them untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
